                      <p><b>Conference Committee</b>
                  
                  <p>Each section of IPRA
                  appoints two representatives to serve on one or more planning
                  subsections of the annual Conference Committee covering
                  programs, operations, CEU monitoring, exhibits, student
                  activities, social, Agency Showcase, spouses’ activities,
                  transportation, publicity, and sponsors. Their service on the
                  Conference Committee involves a variety of tasks including
                  gathering topics ideas for educational sessions, securing
                  session chairpersons, and overseeing the evaluation of
                  sessions.
                  </span>
                </td>
