                      <p style="line-height: 100%"><b>Membership Services/Long
                      Range Planning Committee</b>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr bgcolor="##eeeee"> 
                <td height="10">
                      <span >The Membership
                  Services/Long Range Planning Committee’s goal is to promote
                  more active participation by C &amp; M Section members and
                  conducts a biennial membership survey to determine membership
                  needs and develops ways to meet those needs. This committee
                  oversees the section’s mentoring program which pairs new
                  section members with more experienced professionals in the
                  field.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>The annual
                  Membership Directory and Resource Guide is published by the
                  committee to help section members benefit from their fellow
                  members’ knowledge and experience in the communications and
                  marketing areas.</span><span><o:p>
                      &nbsp;
                  </span>
