                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr bgcolor="##eeeee">
                <td height="10">
                      The Workshop Committee organizes continuing education
                  opportunities to help our section members expand their skills
                  and keep up-to-date on the latest trends and technologies in
                  communications and marketing. Roundtables, hands-on workshops
                  and seminars are provided three or four times each year by
                  presenters and facilitators from within and outside the parks
                  and recreation field. These events offer an arena in which to
